			<h1
				class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-lg font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto"
			>
            Privacy by design
			</h1>
			<!-- <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-400 py-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center md:block hidden">
				Empowering healthcare providers with behavioral analytics that delivers meaningful engagement & evidence-based treatments
			</p> -->
		</div>

		<div class="mt-6 prose prose-indigo prose-lg text-gray-200 mx-auto max-w-2xl md:pb-32 pb-10">
			<div class="text-center space-y-2">
				<div>Since Sahha’s inception, we put user privacy first.</div>	
				<div>We don’t collect 
					<span class="underline underline-offset-1">names</span> , 
					<span class="underline underline-offset-1">emails</span>, 
					<span class="underline underline-offset-1">phone numbers</span>, 
					<span class="underline underline-offset-1">addresses</span> , or
					<span class="underline underline-offset-1">birthdates</span> .</div>
				<div>Your personal information is yours, not ours.</div>	
				<div>And your information is not a product.</div>		
			</div>

			<br>
			<div class="border-b-2 border-sahha-800"></div>
			<p class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-center py-4">
				" Our technology does not and cannot collect personally identifiable information <span class="font-semibold">and never will.</span>  "		
			</p>
			<div class="text-sm text-center">Read our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-[#6BD5FF]">Privacy Policy</a> here for more information about what we collect and why.</div>
